g.text: Chart is still cluttered, but decreasing severity over time is apparent.
To achieve this, vertical sequencing is mapped to severity, and repetitive labels have been moved into the axis guides.
Severity of an unknown disease shown in a Sankey chart
Data has been hand-synthesised to be close to an original plot of unknown provenance.
